* matches zero or more characters:
*.txt
a*.txt
a*


? matches exactly one character
?.txt
?? (matches all two character files)

[] matches any of the characters included

[!] matches not any of the characters included


[a-g] matches a range


predefined name character classes:
[[:alpha:]]  both lower and uppercase alphabetic
[[:alnum:]]  alpha and digits
[[:digit:]]
[[:lower:]]
[[:space:]]  whitespaces including spaces, tabs, and newline
[[:upper:]]


\  escape chacter
